4028075_6193775273117411495_n[1].png", "id": "586326426208537", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974671_586326429541870_8809032610806279492_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=ZjwJI3ar14YQ7kNvgH_m0Cv&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDYm62gfI4a_m1KMUmiGyx6zOH66xNbY8LbuqiALk0FNw&oe=66FD390E"}, "display_name": "Header Goal VR : Being Axel Rix", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Header Goal VR is a physics based, action pumped, virtual reality sports game with a simulation like interaction dynamics. Through its story based levels you find yourself in the place of the character Axel Rix who is a young soccer player. Your main goal is to hit thrown balls by heading while targeting various objects in a soccer training field. Each stage has a unique level design. To achieve a better score, you should have a plan. Even hitting the targets in the right order makes a great difference. You will start feel like Axel within the immersive atmosphere of the game.\n\nBeing able to hit a virtual ball in the most natural and realistic way makes Header Goal VR the most entertaining way of heading a ball.", "short_description": "Header Goal VR is a physics based, action pumped, virtual reality sports game with a simulation like interaction dynamics. Through its story based levels you find yourself in the place of the character Axel Rix who is a young soccer player."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://codemodeon.com/legal/privacy.pdf", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://codemodeon.com/legal/eula.pdf", "publisher_name": "Codemodeon", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://codemodeon.com/headergoalvr", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["CASUAL", "SIMULATION", "SPORTS"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "intern